## Component Conventions (all .astro)

1. No AI-style comments like "Clean, descriptive context label" or
   "Smooth, non-blocking cascading animation delays" — write clean code.
2. Import `styles.css` in frontmatter with `import "./styles.css";`.
3. Use the shared animation keyframes from `styles.css`. Don't redefine.
4. SVG `viewBox` scales responsively. Use `class="block h-auto w-full"`.
5. Every SVG diagram gets `role="img"` with `aria-label`.
6. All colors via Tailwind utility classes (not inline styles).
7. Consistent stroke widths: lines 1.5-2, accent elements 2.5-3.5.
8. Nodes: `r=24` for main, `r=18` for secondary, text `font-bold text-2xl`.

