## Migration Strategy

1. Create directory `emergence/` with new architecture
2. Build shared infrastructure: styles.css, utils.ts, Figure, Callout, StepHeader
3. Write index.mdx with new narrative
4. Port and redesign each diagram component
5. Test rendering
6. When complete, remove old `emergence-complexite/` directory
